Fastigo.text: Telegraph health of Grandmother, shall I come

Fatifer.text: Telegraph health of Husband, shall I come

Fatum.text: Telegraph health of Mother, shall I come

Favilla.text: Telegraph health of Sister, shall I come

Fecialis.text: Telegraph health of Son , shall I come

Felineus.text: Telegraph health of Wife, shall I come

Fellator.text: Telegraph health of yourself, shall I come

Femella.text: Telegraph health of yourself, am very anxious

Fenebris.text: Very much better, do not come, will write

Fenero.text: Very much better, and improving fast

Fenestra.text: Very much better, and improving fast, do not come

Ferio.text: Wound is not healing very rapidly

Ferme.text: Please write fully present condition of patient

Ferrugo.text: Hire a conveyance to meet me at ---
